iku poet († {{ill|1783|ja|1783|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Hōreki|ja|Hōreki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1760|ja|1760|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kawaoka Seishū|ja|華岡青洲|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a physician and pioneer of anesthesia († {{ill|1835|ja|1835|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|lt=Bunka|lt_ja=文化|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 14th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1817|ja|1817|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ono Yūgorō|ja|小野友五郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a mathematician († {{ill|1898|ja|1898|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1849|ja|1849|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Saionji Kinmochi|ja|西園寺公望|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , who served as Prime Minister on two occasions and as genrō († {{ill|1940|ja|1940|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Doi Bansui|ja|土井晩翠|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a poet († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
