2=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 100th emperor of the Northern Court (* {{ill|1377|ja|1377|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1856|ja|1856|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , an agrarian reformer (* {{ill|1787|ja|1787|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
