ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1849|ja|1849|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Saionji Kinmochi|ja|西園寺公望|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , who served as Prime Minister on two occasions and as genrō († {{ill|1940|ja|1940|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Doi Bansui|ja|土井晩翠|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a poet († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
