{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 23''' is the 23rd day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|712|ja|712|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – The region of Echigo split the Dewa district off into a separate Dewa Province. * {{ill|Teiji|ja|貞治|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year/{{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 17th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1362|ja|1362|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 11|ja|10月11日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – The Northern Court changed its era name from {{ill|Kang'an|ja|康安|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to {{ill|Teiji|ja|貞治|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . * {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 12nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1800|ja|1800|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – Inō Tadataka completed his survey of Ezo and the Ōshū Kaidō, then returned to Edo and presented his preliminary map to the shogunate. * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1857|ja|1857|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – U.S. 