ter on two occasions and as genrō († {{ill|1940|ja|1940|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Doi Bansui|ja|土井晩翠|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a poet († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
