'''September 23''' is the 23rd day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . 


== Events ==
* {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|712|ja|712|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – The region of Echigo split the Dewa district off into a separate Dewa Province.
* {{ill|Teiji|ja|貞治|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year/{{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 17th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1362|ja|1362|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 11|ja|10月11日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – The Northern Court changed its era name from {{ill|Kang'an|ja|康安|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  to {{ill|Teiji|ja|貞治|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .
* {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 12nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1800|ja|1800|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – Inō Tadataka completed his survey of Ezo and the Ōshū Kaidō, then returned to Edo and presented his preliminary map to the shogunate.
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1857|ja|1857|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – U.S. Consul {{ill|Townsend Harris|ja|ハリス|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  visited Edo Castle and met with Tokugawa Iesada.
== Births ==
* {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 15th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1702|ja|1702|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 24|ja|10月24日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Yokoi Yayuu|ja|横井也有|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a haiku poet († {{ill|1783|ja|1783|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Hōreki|ja|Hōreki|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 10th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1760|ja|1760|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Kawaoka Seishū|ja|華岡青洲|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a physician and pioneer of anesthesia († {{ill|1835|ja|1835|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|lt=Bunka|lt_ja=文化|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 14th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1817|ja|1817|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Ono Yūgorō|ja|小野友五郎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a mathematician († {{ill|1898|ja|1898|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1849|ja|1849|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Saionji Kinmochi|ja|西園寺公望|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , who served as Prime Minister on two occasions and as genrō († {{ill|1940|ja|1940|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Doi Bansui|ja|土井晩翠|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a poet († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).

