* {{ill|Taihei Kōkoku|ja|太平興国|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|976|ja|976|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Zhao Kuangyin|ja|趙匡胤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Taizu), the first emperor of the Northern Song (* {{ill|927|ja|927|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
