|qq=}} {{ill|976|ja|976|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/976|qq=}} {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 14|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Zhao Kuangyin|ja|趙匡胤|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Zhao Kuangyin|qq=}} (Taizu), the first emperor of the Northern Song (* {{ill|927|ja|927|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/927|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Daiji (Japan)|ja|大治|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daiji (Japan)|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1127|ja|1127|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1127|qq=}} {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 25|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshimitsu|ja|源義光|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoshimitsu|qq=}} , a military commander and younger brother of {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshiie|ja|源義家|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoshiie|qq=}} (* {{ill|1045|ja|1045|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1045|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eikyō|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1433|ja|1433|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1433|qq=}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 1|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Komatsu|ja|後小松天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Go-Komatsu|qq=}} , the 100th emperor of the Northern Court (* {{ill|1377|ja|1377|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1377|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1856|ja|1856|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1856|qq=}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 17|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ninomiya Sontoku|qq=}} , an agrarian reformer (* {{ill|1787|ja|1787|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1787|qq=}} ).
