12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1898|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ). * [[:en:Kaei|Kaei]] 2nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1849|1849]] [[:en:December 7|December 7]] ） – [[:en:Saionji Kinmochi|Saionji Kinmochi]] , who served as Prime Minister on two occasions and as genrō († {{ill|1940|ja|1940|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1940|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ). * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 4th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1871|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} [[:en:December 5|December 5]] ） – {{ill|Doi Bansui|ja|土井晩翠|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Doi Bansui|qq=}} , a poet († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1952|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} ).
